data.description: Outstanding opportunity! Live in one home and rent the other - or perfect for mother-in-law separate quarters. With 2274SF main home with 3 beds/2 full baths and 960SF in what's affectionately known as the casita. All this on 16+ acres with seasonal pond, just 5 minutes to downtown DeFuniak Springs. Every part of this estate has been exceptionally maintained. You'll adore this spacious, well thought out kitchen with loads of space. Included is a huge 19x19 hobby room for home biz, school, etc. Large dining area for family gatherings. Covered back porch overlooking your seasonal pond. The casita is 2 floors with 1-2 bedrooms depending on use, w/ full kitchen & bath on main floor. Additional storage buildings & covered parking. This is the picture of privacy and self sustaining lifestyle.
